# 📈 Portfolio Optimization using ML and Financial APIs

> An end-to-end full-stack application that uses Machine Learning models and real-time Financial APIs to predict stock returns, optimize portfolio allocation, and deliver technical analysis — all through a clean, interactive web interface.

